title: DCCI’s former president Shahjahan Khan no more
name: Daily Sun
description: Mohammad Shahjahan Khan, former President of Dhaka Chamber of Commerce and Industry, breathed his last on Monday, 22nd May, in Bangkok, Thailand. He died at 11:40 pm Bangladesh time while undergoing treatment
